  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"StartFraction 12 x plus 28 Over 4 EndFraction minus StartFraction s Over 13 EndFraction equals r left parenthesis x minus 8 right parenthesis\"><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mn>12</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mrow><mn>28</mn></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>4</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mi>s</mi><mrow><mn>13</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>r</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mrow><mn>8</mn></mrow></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In the given equation, <math alttext=\"s\"><mi>s</mi>\n</math> and <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math> are constants, and <math alttext=\"s greater than 0\"><mi>s</mi><mo>&#62;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>. If the equation has infinitely many solutions, what is the value of <math alttext=\"s\"><mi>s</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
